projectM engine - libprojectM
-------------------------------------

You need OpenGL and CMake to compile libprojectM. You will need FTGL (truetype fonts) if you want the on-screen display.

----ON LINUX, BSD, SOLARIS, ETC.---

cmake . (-or-) ccmake .
make
make install 

You may change compile options via cmake or ccmake to enable/disable FTGL, FrameBuffer Objects, or Debug printouts.

----ON MAC OR WIN32---

You'll find project files for XCode, Visual Studio, etc in SVN. 

--------------------------------------------
